cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques for binarization of multispectral images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of evolutionary optimization and ensemble methods could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves preprocessing techniques, which could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of state-of-the-art binarization methods could also be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
